	keywords = {resilience, boundary work},
	annote = {Not particularly interesting.   Shows the term is used in lots of fields with little cross-citation.  SES lit is the partial exception, with it reaching out to others, but still anchored in ecology.   Not a lot of evidence that the concept bridges economic and ecologic, or social and natural science ways of thinking. 
